window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Black Arbor Convention is a secret society of the most ruthless killers in the world.</p> <p>We gather.... We follow the rules.... We indulge in our desire to shed blood once a year. Then, we return to our normal lives. Well, the rest of the members do. Not the king of the Brotherhood. Not me. I’m not allowed, but I’ve never been so tempted to break the rules set by my father.... Not until now.</p> <p>I'm deadly.</p> <p>Dangerous.</p> <p>My fixation will lead to both of our ruin should I get too close.... Yet, I can't help myself.</p> <p>Warning: This book has content that might be triggering to some listeners and is intended for audiences 18+.</p>"; 
